title: Let The Players Vote! | Best of I AM ATHLETE Tonight Week Four
description: This week on I AM ATHLETE Tonight, the guys chat about what makes a superstar; Joel Embiid getting snubbed as a member of 1st team All-NBA; players should have more influence on Hall of Fame and postseason award voting and a chat on Ravens QB Lamar Jackson missing OTAs.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Brandon Marshall, Adam 'Pac Man' Jones, Omar Kelly, Brandon Flowers, Antione Walker)
